.git
src/vendor
src/node_modules
# Runtime storage tree — recreated by the entrypoint inside the
# container and bind-mounted at runtime, so the build context never
# needs these. Excluding them also dodges the common host-side
# permission trap where `src/storage/app/attachments` ends up owned
# by the in-container www-data uid (82) and becomes unreadable by
# the host build user, which would otherwise abort `docker build`
# with "error from sender: ... permission denied".
src/storage/app/attachments
src/storage/framework
src/storage/logs/*
src/.phpunit.cache
unit_tests
API_tests
run_tests.sh
